FBIS4-12962 "drnes073_n_94002" FBIS-NES-94-073 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 LEBANON U.S. Envoy Delivers Message to Buwayz U.S. Envoy Delivers Message to Buwayz NC1504111694 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1030 GMT 15 Apr 94 NC1504111694 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Excerpt] A short time ago, U.S. Ambassador to Beirut Mark Hambley handed Foreign Minister Faris Buwayz a message from the U.S. Government asking that security and calm be established on the Lebanese border. [passage omitted]
